Package: sleeper
Title: Esimate Sleep Status from Accelerometry Data
Version: 0.01
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "John",
           family = "Muschelli",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "muschellij2@gmail.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-6469-1750"))
Description: Wraps the classifier from the paper 
  <https://doi.org/10.1038/s41598-020-79217-x> and associated code from
  <https://github.com/wadpac/Sundararajan-SleepClassification-2021/blob/master/ggir_ext>.
  Users must download the model files from <https://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3752645>
  in order to use this method.
